Package: dsImaging
Title: DataSHIELD Medical Imaging Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(person("David", "Sarrat González", , "david.sarrat@isglobal.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Xavier", "Escribà-Montagut", , "xavier.escriba@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")),
      person("Juan R", "González", , "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org", role = c("aut")))
Description: Modular framework for distributed medical imaging analysis using
    DataSHIELD infrastructure. Connects vault storage (dsVault) with HPC
    processing (dsHPC) to extract radiomic features from medical images.
    Supports lung segmentation (lungmask) and radiomic feature extraction
    (pyradiomics) pipelines.
